Thumbs.db

# Cloudflare/Wrangler local cache
**/.wrangler/

# Firmware build artifacts
firmware/.pio/
.pio/
firmware/src/*.ino.cpp

# Local editor/workspace state
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/

